{"tid":1164713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"縮骨遮當武器　廢老怒打輕鐵　只因想𢱑番上車？","createTime":"2019-05-21T10:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T17:55:53.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e56109dab16695b4beb408dc1006c30bc298e38d","tid":1164713,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T10:02:22.000Z","msg":"縮骨遮當武器 阿婆怒打輕鐵 只因想𢱑番上車？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WYgon4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WYgon4&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=6d0568a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WYgon4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190521/photo/bkn-20190521173306059-0521_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190521175748\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190521%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190521173306059-0521_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190521175748&h=c3d8755e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等幾分鐘都唔得？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從Facebook群組「天水圍友」的影片可見，周一（20日）在輕鐵天耀站，一名婆婆手持縮骨遮不停敲打車門。即使列車其後緩緩駛離月台，她仍然「鍥而不捨」。期間有數名途人曾嘗試勸止婆婆，並將婆婆帶離列車附近，惟婆婆仍不斷掙扎。"},{"pid":"dc14df28d3ee18921845cbff5d3c5e3bf69d5c72","tid":1164713,"uid":205098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T10:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0581c2ebce14295026a1e5c59b391675a431d484","tid":1164713,"uid":235727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"如果我係隔離見到都咪話唔驚，俾佢扑中真係冇仇報"},{"pid":"1d2425c9f6359035360ff00b32bf2bfb5627109f","tid":1164713,"uid":229638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}